u can rock thru some xp</i><br><br>Look above on my status about enchanters and clerics but to get the most experience in a group an enchanter and cleric can make it very efficient.<br><br><i>5 Pets are nice but dont depend on them to kill the beast for you and turn taunt off it will keep em alive longer</i><br><br>AGREE! The shaman pets are not magician pets or necromancer pets you can't let them tank for awhile. Our pets have little HP, they do help but never depend on them.<br><br><i>6 Always keep regen up and use cloro you get manna back alot faster with out it it will take forever&lt;poor mans crack=p&gt;</i><br><br>I assume you mean keep chloroplast up so you can cannabalize?<br><br><i>7 max your wisdiom out you need as much as you can our spells are costly</i><br><br>Our slow series is a huge taunt and sometimes taking some AC Gear over Wisdom Gear can help. Wisdom over 200 doesn't give you any more mana. The AC/Wisdom is more a preference though and whichever works better for you.<br><br><i>8 Keep all your weapon skills up 1 and 2hb and pericing you get some wicked and i mean wicked weapons at higher levels.</i><br><br>We do have some nice weapons at high levels but it isn't <b>that</b> important. We could do a lot more damage with DoTs or if you are lucky a Jaundiced Bone Bracer.<br>&nbsp;<br>Mairu O'Die<br>Level 60 Barbarian Oracle<br>Master Alchemist(170)<br>Bristlebane Server</td></tr>
